Resist Poison, Resist Cold, Resist Lightning, Resist Fire

An experienced druid often grows resistant to elemental
attacks and to creatures' poisons.  Each of these
powers, which must be separately acquired, grants the
druid a resistance to the specified attack form.  If
fully mastered, the druid is all but immune to such
attacks, and (for cold and fire) may travel with
impunity in Hyperborea or Souvrael.  These powers do
nothing about other types of damage, however -- a
druid bitten by a snake may be resistant to poison,
but he will still be injured by the teeth.

Command: none necessary
Base Cost: none
Base Recovery: none
Base Effect: protection (moderate)
Base Duration: permanent
Guild Level: 14-17
